- I'm not going to say, but more than that.

190
00:12:35,195 --> 00:12:37,945
I apologize you had
to find out this way.

191
00:12:38,323 --> 00:12:40,297
Believe me,
it wasn't my decision.

192
00:12:45,233 --> 00:12:46,981
