but they were under the belief

228
00:14:42,762 --> 00:14:45,559
that P.P.L.
was being sold as well.

229
00:14:45,872 --> 00:14:48,152
- And what did you tell them?
- <i>That they were wrong.</i>

230
00:14:48,153 --> 00:14:50,449
They even wanted to bid
for Sterling Cooper--

231
00:14:50,450 --> 00:14:52,559
12% above
our purchase price.

232
00:14:55,488 --> 00:14:58,497
Listen,
I apologize, lane.

233
00:14:58,693 --> 00:15:01,002
Obviously the news
is getting out.

234
00:15:01,593 --> 00:15:04,904
- What news?
- P.P.L. is being sold as well.

235
00:15:05,861 --> 00:15:10,781
