- Didn't seem pertinent.

236
00:15:10,782 --> 00:15:13,490
Trying to keep our company
calm as well as theirs.

237
00:15:13,491 --> 00:15:17,716
- Well, where's my place in this?
- With McCann, I suppose.

238
00:15:18,951 --> 00:15:22,799
There there, lane. They know you're 
essential to the transition.

239
